516
00:28:44,839 --> 00:28:46,160
Kamu ini manusia...

517
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:50,719
Apa maksud lelaki hadiahkan
uncang wangi kepada perempuan?

518
00:28:52,359 --> 00:28:53,520
Sudah tentu

519
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:54,680
menyukai!

520
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:56,439
Kenapa dengan awak?

521
00:28:57,439 --> 00:28:58,400
Tak apa-apa.

522
00:29:01,560 --> 00:29:02,959
(Tak mungkin.)

523
00:29:20,119 --> 00:29:22,239
Jangan berpura-pura, dungunya.

524
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:25,079
Mengapa awak lagi?

525
00:29:27,359 --> 00:29:29,040
Mengapa saya lagi?

526
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:33,119
Agaknya Tuan Xue amat kecewa
apabila jumpa saya.

527
00:29:33,479 --> 00:29:34,280
Betul.

528
00:29:36,239 --> 00:29:38,880
Nampaknya, awak tak jumpa dia.

529
00:29:40,239 --> 00:29:41,000
Dah jumpa.

530
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:42,400
Namun, tidak dipanggil?

531
00:29:44,479 --> 00:29:47,079
Ini terbukti, Ayu tidak
hadapi masalah hari ini.

532
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,040
Tak betul.

533
00:29:50,359 --> 00:29:51,640
Hari ini, dia hadapi masalah.

534
00:29:51,839 --> 00:29:52,839
Namun, dia tak pernah fikir

535
00:29:52,959 --> 00:29:54,479
nak panggil saya.

536
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:57,959
Jadi, Raja Naga rasa

537
