546
00:30:30,199 --> 00:30:31,599
Dulu, dia bernama Long Qingqing.

547
00:30:31,719 --> 00:30:33,199
Sudah tentu saya abangnya.

548
00:30:34,079 --> 00:30:37,520
Sekarang, dia bernama Xue Qingqing.

549
00:30:37,760 --> 00:30:39,920
Sudah tentu dia tiada hubungan
dengan saya.

550
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:44,479
Ke mana dia akan pergi?

551
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,359
Adakah dia berada di rumah Ayu?

552
00:30:48,959 --> 00:30:49,880
Awak nak pergi jumpa dia?

553
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:50,800
Tak nak.

554
00:30:54,280 --> 00:30:55,640
Awak tunggu perlahan-lahan.

555
00:31:26,119 --> 00:31:27,719
(Mengapa awak tak panggil saya?)

556
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:30,040
(Di mana bekas kelip-kelip?)

557
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:34,160
(Adakah)

558
00:31:34,719 --> 00:31:35,680
